title: 820-00281 no audio
message:
Cant find any liquid damage.

Same issue on clients macOS, Bootcamp and on mine external macOS.
No audio.

In system preferences > Sound Output and Input shows 'No devices found"
On touchbar volume buttons are grayed out.

Headphones not detected when plugged in.

U6400/40 and U6500/50 got power rails present.
AUD_SPKRAMP_RESET_L got only 0.01V

R6401 got correct resistnace.

U6200 got power rails present
AUD_CODEC_INT_L 1.8V
AUD_SPKRAMP_INT_L 1.8V
SPK_IDO 1.8V

Any idea?

title: 820-00281 no audio
message:
Removed U6200 and all pads are connected with rest of the board, no broken lines.
Replaced U6200 but issue still the same.

Any hope?

title: 820-00281 no audio
message: If reset is OK and all series resistors too, then should be PCH issue...

title: 820-00281 no audio
message: OK, thank you for help anyway :)
